</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Schizoaffective disorder</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox" style="width:22em">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color: lightgrey">Schizoaffective disorder</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Courtyard with Lunatics by Goya 1794.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg/230px-Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg" width="230" height="314" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg/345px-Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg/460px-Courtyard_with_Lunatics_by_Goya_1794.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1498" data-file-height="2045" /></a>
<div>Having had auditory hallucinations and depression, <a href="/wiki/Francisco_Goya" title="Francisco Goya">Francisco Goya</a> painted <i><a href="/wiki/Yard_with_Lunatics" title="Yard with Lunatics">Yard with Lunatics</a></i> in 1794.</div>
</td>
</tr>
