<div class="reflist" style="list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Seasonal_affective_disorder" title="Seasonal affective disorder">Seasonal Affective Disorder</a> or <a href="/wiki/Social_anxiety_disorder" title="Social anxiety disorder">Social Anxiety Disorder</a>, which are also commonly abbreviated SAD.</span></li>
